We may process your personal data for the following purposes:
 • To provide our services in accordance with the applicable terms and conditions;
 • To manage the business relationship with you and the client of AG Assurance Genevoise SA that you represent;
 • To develop and improve our services;
 In order to provide information and offers to current or potential clients of AG Assurance Genevoise SA regarding our solution through selected third parties. Any marketing material sent using your personal data is directed to you as a legal entity representing a current or potential client of AG Assurance Genevoise SA, and not to you as a private individual.
